summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning, amending Plat 221E, page 8 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone the property located at 14352 Lake City Way N.E. from Single Family 7200 (SF7200) to Neighborhood Commercial 2 with a thirty-foot height limitation (NC2/30') and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of Village Seattle Partners, C.F. 300552, Appl. 9501363)
